column2:
"HAHAHAHA!
So you've endured the fight,
even with the two of us!"

"You're an amazing person!
I wonder how long it took
you to reach that power!"

"Hah, it's an honor to receive
your praise. You're probably the
only one to notice that this
is the fruit of hard labor."

"While I do wish we could keep
on going, it seems some business
has cropped up."

"We will continue this another
time. Think of this as setting
the stage for next time. Until then."

"We were supposed to be on the look
out for a dangerous Phantom, but we
ended up encountering something far worse."

"Even during the fight, she did not seem
serious at all. To be quite honest,
she's incomprehensible."

"But wow, this world is a huge place!
I'm happy that I've yet a long ways
to go! It'll be worth it! "
